{"tid":1976090,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"一句講晒，信「聖經」定信「歷史科學家」","createTime":"2020-04-17T03:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T16:41:31.000Z","uid":149978,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1561bfef16a8de52254bf5c290d448a9c72c6c1e","tid":1976090,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:58:41.000Z","msg":"聖經：「<strong>我們一生的年日是七十歲</strong>，若是強壯可到八十歲；但其中所矜誇的，不過是勞苦愁煩，轉眼成空，我們便如飛而去。」（詩篇90：10）（<strong>寫於</strong>公元前1000年，即係<strong>3000年前</strong>）<br />\n<br />\n科學家：從DNA分析，古代人僅能活到38歲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ctee.com.tw/news/biotech/191689.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fctee.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbiotech%2F191689.html&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU93yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=133a9e46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ctee.com.tw/news/biotech/191689.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />信聖經：一般古人根本可以活到七十歲。班現代人想借科學自high，屈古人短命短壽，借此大讚自己文明好發達好勁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />信歷史科學家，古人講大話。現代科學話古人30歲就30歲，何來有70歲。騙人。"},{"pid":"1f1afb4166fb4e6b8a5b5a58f2921b5f73459b18","tid":1976090,"uid":324712,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:04:14.000Z","msg":"古代:三十萬軍號稱百萬軍<br />\n咁三十歲號稱七十歲好似唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e2f5c451dc2c04295616c1b187c7c3c79980f8","tid":1976090,"uid":50588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:05:24.000Z","msg":"聖經遲過&ldquo;古人&rdquo;好多喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41faa5e051851d6a9c5b304706be5ccc3ad77e88","tid":1976090,"uid":277186,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:06:39.000Z","msg":"歷史書只係謊言合集"},{"pid":"9390424f0da50cd4cd7134628607876f093a5476","tid":1976090